<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Kitchen Guru - Recipe Details</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;0,9..144,700;1,9..144,400&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    /* ============================================
       KITCHENGURU - RECIPE SHOW PAGE
       Warm Mocha Brown Theme
       ============================================ */

    :root {
      /* Mocha Brown Palette - Deliberately darker to remain mocha on brightened screens */
      --mocha-darkest: #2c1810;
      --mocha-dark: #3d251a;
      --mocha-medium: #4a2c1c;
      --mocha-base: #5c3a2e;
      --mocha-light: #7a5244;
      --mocha-lighter: #9b7566;

      /* Background Colors */
      --bg-primary: #f8f4f1;
      --bg-secondary: #f0e9e4;
      --bg-tertiary: #e8dfd8;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;

      /* Accent Colors */
      --accent-primary: #c4704a;
      --accent-secondary: #d4a574;
      --accent-tertiary: #8b5a3c;
      --accent-danger: #b85450;

      /* Shadows */
      --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(44, 24, 16, 0.08);
      --shadow-card: 0 4px 20px rgba(44, 24, 16, 0.06);
      --shadow-card-hover: 0 12px 40px rgba(44, 24, 16, 0.12);

      /* Border */
      --border-color: rgba(92, 58, 46, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      color: var(--mocha-darkest);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    /* Subtle background texture */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 50% at 20% 20%, rgba(196, 112, 74, 0.03) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 80% 80%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    /* ============================================
       NAVBAR
       ============================================ */

    header.border-bottom {
      background: var(--bg-card) !important;
      border-bottom-color: var(--border-color) !important;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    .navbar {
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .navbar-brand img {
      height: 36px;
      width: auto;
    }

    .navbar-brand span {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--mocha-dark);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .navbar-nav {
      align-items: center;
    }

    .navbar-nav .nav-link {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--mocha-base);
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover {
      color: var(--mocha-dark);
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
    }

    .navbar-nav .nav-link.active {
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      background: rgba(196, 112, 74, 0.08);
    }

    .user-avatar {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--mocha-base), var(--mocha-light));
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 50%;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
    }

    .user-avatar:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(92, 58, 46, 0.25);
    }

    /* ============================================
       ANIMATIONS
       ============================================ */

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* ============================================
       MAIN CONTENT
       ============================================ */

    #main-content {
      min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
      animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
    }

    /* ============================================
       BUTTONS
       ============================================ */

    .btn {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      transition: all 0.25s ease;
      border-radius: 50px;
    }

    .btn-outline-secondary {
      color: var(--mocha-base);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border-color);
      background: transparent;
    }

    .btn-outline-secondary:hover {
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
      border-color: var(--mocha-light);
      color: var(--mocha-dark);
    }

    .btn-outline-danger {
      color: var(--accent-danger);
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(184, 84, 80, 0.4);
      background: transparent;
    }

    .btn-outline-danger:hover {
      background: var(--accent-danger);
      border-color: var(--accent-danger);
      color: white;
    }

    .btn-sm {
      padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    /* ============================================
       RECIPE DETAIL CARD
       ============================================ */

    .recipe-container {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .action-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      animation: fadeInUp 0.4s ease-out;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      animation: fadeInUp 0.5s ease-out 0.1s both;
    }

    .card-body {
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    /* Recipe Title */
    .recipe-title {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--mocha-darkest);
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* Recipe Description */
    .recipe-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--mocha-light);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Time Badges */
    .time-badges {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .time-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--mocha-lighter);
    }

    .time-badge .icon {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .time-badge .value {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--mocha-base);
    }

    .time-badge .label {
      color: var(--mocha-lighter);
    }

    /* Divider */
    hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    /* Section Titles */
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--mocha-dark);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    /* Placeholder Text */
    .placeholder-text {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--mocha-lighter);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Ingredients List (for future use) */
    .ingredients-list {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .ingredients-list li {
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      color: var(--mocha-base);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .ingredients-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .ingredients-list li::before {
      content: '•';
      color: var(--accent-primary);
      margin-right: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Steps List (for future use) */
    .steps-list {
      counter-reset: step-counter;
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .steps-list li {
      counter-increment: step-counter;
      padding: 1rem 0;
      padding-left: 3rem;
      position: relative;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      color: var(--mocha-base);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .steps-list li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .steps-list li::before {
      content: counter(step-counter);
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 1rem;
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-primary), var(--accent-tertiary));
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ============================================
       RESPONSIVE
       ============================================ */

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .card-body {
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .recipe-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .action-row {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .action-row .btn {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .time-badges {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.75rem;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .navbar-brand span {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .navbar-nav .nav-link {
        padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
    }

    /* ============================================
       REDUCED MOTION
       ============================================ */

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
        transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAVBAR -->
  <header class="border-bottom bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect width="36" height="36" rx="8" fill="url(#mocha-gradient)"/>
            <path d="M10 18C10 14 12 11 18 11C24 11 26 14 26 18" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="18" cy="22" r="4" fill="white"/>
            <path d="M14 26H22" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="mocha-gradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="36" y2="36" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                <stop stop-color="#5c3a2e"/>
                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#7a5244"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
          </svg>
          <span>Kitchen Guru</span>
        </a>

        <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
          <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
          <a class="nav-link active" href="index.html">My Recipes</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/meal-plans">Meal Plans</a>
          <div class="dropdown-toggle user-avatar ms-3">JD</div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- MAIN CONTENT: SHOW PAGE -->
  <main id="main-content" class="py-4">
    <div class="container py-5 recipe-container">

      <!-- Back + delete actions -->
      <div class="action-row">
        <a href="index.html" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded-pill">
          ← Back to my recipes
        </a>
        <button class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm rounded-pill" onclick="confirm('Remove this recipe from your cookbook?')">
          Delete this recipe
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- Recipe card -->
      <div class="card shadow-sm border-0 rounded-4">
        <div class="card-body p-4">
          <h1 class="recipe-title">Morning Chia Seed Bowl with 5 Plants</h1>
          <p class="recipe-description">A nutrient-dense breakfast bowl packed with fiber, omega-3s, and plant-based protein. Perfect for busy mornings when you need sustained energy without the crash.</p>

          <div class="time-badges">
            <div class="time-badge">
              <span class="icon">⏱</span>
              <span class="value">5 min</span>
              <span class="label">prep</span>
            </div>
            <div class="time-badge">
              <span class="icon">🔥</span>
              <span class="value">0 min</span>
              <span class="label">cook</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <hr>

          <!-- Ingredients Section -->
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h2 class="section-title">Ingredients</h2>
            <p class="placeholder-text">
              Coming soon – we'll display structured ingredients here.
            </p>
            <!-- Example of future ingredients list:
            <ul class="ingredients-list">
              <li>3 tbsp chia seeds</li>
              <li>1 cup almond milk</li>
              <li>1 tbsp maple syrup</li>
              <li>1/2 cup mixed berries</li>
              <li>1 tbsp hemp seeds</li>
            </ul>
            -->
          </div>

          <!-- Steps Section -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Steps</h2>
            <p class="placeholder-text">
              Coming soon – we'll show step-by-step instructions here.
            </p>
            <!-- Example of future steps list:
            <ol class="steps-list">
              <li>Combine chia seeds and almond milk in a bowl or jar. Stir well to prevent clumping.</li>
              <li>Add maple syrup and stir again. Cover and refrigerate overnight or for at least 2 hours.</li>
              <li>When ready to serve, give it a good stir. The mixture should be thick and pudding-like.</li>
              <li>Top with mixed berries and hemp seeds. Enjoy cold!</li>
            </ol>
            -->
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
